@subsubsection{(Co)Slice Category}

A @deftech{slice category} (@deftech{over category}) @math{ùíû/c} is a construction
that allows us to study a @tech{category} @math{ùíû} through the lens of a fixed
@tech{object} @math{c} in @math{ùíû}. Intuitively, @math{ùíû/c} consists of all
the @tech{objects} and @tech{morphisms} in @math{ùíû} that are "over" @math{c}.

@math{ùíû/c} is constructed by takeing @math{ùíû}'s @tech{morphisms} end to @math{c}
as @tech{objects}, and @tech{commutative triangles} end to @math{c} as @tech{morphisms}.

